Find out what time the next trains for my destination station leave

Narrative:
In order to plan my trips more effectively
As a commuter
I want to know the next trains going to my destination

Scenario: Find the optimal route between stations on the same line
Given Western line trains from Warsaw leave for Bydgoszcz at 7:00, 7:50, 8:00
When I want to travel from Warsaw to Bydgoszcz at 7:30
Then I should be told about the trains at: 7:50, 8:00
